data.description: MUST SEE to admire its entire layout. Home currently has a total of 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms.  Currently divided as a 3/2 (main home) and an additional 1bd/1bth separate quarters or can rent out or can be easily converted back to a 4/3 home. Plus, an additional 1/1 that allows you to rent out with a private entrance. The entire concrete flooring has ample space for boats, RV, Trailers, and sheds. Enjoy an updated modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, modern bathrooms, and large covered patio for your outdoor entertainment with room for a pool. Updated Electrical, AC and Roof. Minutes to all your shopping needs and close to Turnpike and US1. Tax roll reflects 3bed/1bath. There will be a closing incentive with our preferred lender.  Seller motivated, bring all offers.
